a%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fus.macmillan.com%2Fbooks%2F9781250284297%2Fcobaltred%5C%22%3ECobalt%20Red%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20author%20Siddharth%20Kara%20describes%20a%20modern%20geopolitical%20quandary.%20Half%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20reserves%20of%20cobalt%20lie%20in%20a%20400%20sqkm%20crescent%20running%20from%20the%20Democratic%20Republic%20of%20the%20Congo%20(DRC)%20to%20northern%20Zambia%2C%20writes%20Kara%20in%20his%20book%20about%20the%20unfettered%20mining%20of%20the%20mineral%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20the%20mining%20here%20%E2%80%93%20from%20the%20depots%20that%20collect%20cobalt%20ore%20from%20miners%20to%20the%20units%20that%20process%20it%20%E2%80%93%20is%20dominated%20by%20the%20Chinese.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20of%20my%20last%20ground%20count%20in%20November%202021%2C%20there%20were%20nineteen%20major%20industrial%20copper-cobalt%20mining%20complexes%20operating%20in%20(Congo%E2%80%99s)%20Haut-Katanga%20and%20Lualala%20provinces%2C%20fifteen%20of%20which%20were%20owned%20or%20financed%20by%20Chinese%20mining%20companies%2C%E2%80%9D%20writes%20Kara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20just%20the%20start.%20Semi-processed%20cobalt%20from%20these%20mines%20is%20exported%20to%20commercial-grade%20refiners%2C%20most%20of%20whom%20are%20in%20China.%20%E2%80%9CIn%202021%2C%20China%20produced%2075%20percent%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20refined%20cobalt%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20writes.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20single%20largest%20refiner%20was%20Huayou%20Cobalt%20with%20a%20market%20share%20of%2022%20percent.%20Huayou%20owns%20Congo%20Dongfang%20Mining%2C%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20copper-cobalt%20companies%20operating%20in%20the%20DRC.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECobalt%20is%20far%20from%20an%20exception.%20Over%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsws.org%2Fen%2Farticles%2F2023%2F06%2F20%2Fmine-j20.html%5C%22%3Epast%2020%20years%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20China%20has%20methodically%20amassed%20mining%20concessions%20for%20the%20critical%20minerals%20necessary%20for%20the%20energy%20transition%20as%20well%20as%20built%20expertise%20in%20processing%20raw%20ores%20into%20refined%20metals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIEA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iea.org%2Freports%2Fthe-role-of-critical-minerals-in-clean-energy-transitions%2Fexecutive-summary%5C%22%3Eestimates%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20China%E2%80%99s%20share%20of%20refining%20is%20around%2050-70%25%20for%20lithium%20and%20cobalt%2C%2035%25%20for%20nickel%2C%20and%2095%25%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mining.com%2Fweb%2Fcritical-minerals-take-central-stage-in-us-china-rivalry%2F%5C%22%3Emanganese%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20nation%20is%20also%20responsible%20for%20nearly%2090%25%20of%20rare%20earth%20elements%2C%20which%20are%20essential%20raw%20materials%20for%20permanent%20magnets%20used%20in%20wind%20turbines%20and%20EV%20motors%2C%20as%20well%20as%20100%25%20of%20graphite%2C%20the%20anode%20material%20in%20EV%20batteries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20know%2C%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20choke-hold%20over%20the%20global%20energy%20transition%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20end%20there.%20Once%20refined%2C%20cobalt%20and%20lithium%20are%20merged%20with%20other%20metals%20to%20make%20batteries.%20At%20this%20time%2C%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcnevpost.com%2F2023%2F05%2F04%2Fglobal-ev-battery-market-share-q1%2F%5C%22%3E35%3C%2Fa%3E%25%20share%2C%20the%20largest%20lithium-ion%20(Li-Ion)%20battery%20manufacturer%20in%20the%20world%20is%20China%E2%80%99s%20CATL.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20BYD%20overtook%20LG%20to%20claim%2C%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpandaily.com%2Fbyd-surpasses-lg-to-become-worlds-second-largest-ev-battery-supplier%2F%5C%22%3E16%25%20market%20share%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20second%20slot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENor%20is%20that%20all.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Findia-s-first-critical-mineral-list-a-road-towards-supply-chain-security-123062900547_1.html%5C%22%3EFive