0these%20fleet%20customers.%20Whether%20it's%20for%20a%20local%20mom-and-pop%20delivery%20shop%20or%20a%20car%20rental%20firm%20or%20a%20contracting%20company%2C%20EVs%20make%20sense%20for%20moving%20goods%20and%20services%20because%20of%20the%20more%20predictable%20mileage%20and%20use%20cases.%20Charging%20can%20be%20done%20in%20batches%20and%20at%20scheduled%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20going%20electric%20is%20also%20a%20huge%20commitment.%20Not%20only%20does%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartups-poised-to-cash-in-electric-truck-van-market-2022-4%5C%22%3Ebuying%20EVs%20look%20to%20be%20a%20substantial%20upfront%20cost%20to%20fleet%20owners%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20are%20also%20logistical%20pains%20to%20be%20worked%20through%20as%20it%20relates%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeet-dozens-of-startups-leading-the-electric-car-charging-market-2022-2%5C%22%3Echarging%20infrastructure%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20managing%20the%20fleet%20with%20needs%20that%20differ%20from%20one%20fueled%20by%20gas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFleet%20owners%20are%20largely%20financially%20motivated%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0whether%20related%20to%20compliance%20requirements%20or%20tax%20breaks%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20if%20they%20go%20electric%20after%20all%20of%20these%20hurdles%2C%20they%20want%20to%20know%20they're%20sitting%20on%20a%20good%20investment.%20The%20price%20war%20throws%20a%20wrench%20at%20that.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20buy%2010%20F-150%20Lightnings%20at%20%2465%2C000%20and%20then%20you%20wake%20up%20the%20next%20morning%20and%20they're%20%2455%2C000%2C%20you're%20probably%20going%20to%20think%20twice%20about%20replacing%20more%20%5Binternal%20combustion%20engine%5D%20trucks%20with%20an%20EV%20%E2%80%94%20or%20look%20elsewhere%2C%26quot%3B%20Robby%20DeGraff%2C%20AutoPacific%20analyst%2C%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20watching%20your%20numbers%2C%20you're%20watching%20your%20budget%2C%20you're%20watching%20the%