20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKantrowitz%5C%22%20data-remove-tab-index%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKantrowitz%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22summary_bullets%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3EAlex%20Kantrowitz%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22bold%5C%22%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EKantrowitz%20calls%20the%20%26quot%3BTwitter%20clone%26quot%3B%20everything%20ad%20buyers%20looks%20for%20in%20a%20partner.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETheir%20enthusiasm%20has%20little%20to%20do%20with%20content%20moderation%20or%20the%20culture%20war%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20about%20money.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20hasn't%20opened%20Threads%C2%A0to%20ads%20yet%2C%20but%20it%20might%20not%20be%20able%20to%20resist%20for%20long.%20Advertisers%20are%20eager%20to%20spend%20serious%20money%20there%C2%A0and%20are%20already%20planning%20for%20the%20eventuality%2C%20with%20a%20good%20number%20expecting%20the%20opportunity%20to%20arrive%20later%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthreads-never-replace-twitter-meta-zuckerberg-musk-advertisers-brands-influencers-2023-7%5C%22%3EThe%20Twitter%20clone%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20everything%20ad%20buyers%20look%20for%20in%20a%20partner%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-threads-twitter-rival-social-media-2023-7%3F_gl%3D1*14xoxfm*_ga*Mzk1NDUxOTQwLjE2Nzc2MDYyMzg.*_ga_E21CV80ZCZ*MTY5MDQwNTAzNS4yNzMuMS4xNjkwNDA1MDQ5LjQ2LjAuMA..%5C%22%3EA%20large%20audience%2C%20public%20interest%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20potential%20access%20to%20Meta's%20industry-leading%20advertising%20tools.%20And%20as%20soon%20as%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20welcomes%20them%2C%20they%20won't%20waste%20a%20minute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20start%20immediately%20for%20our%20clients%2C%20as%20soon%20as%20advertisements%20are%20available%20on%20Threads%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ahmet%20Yavuz%2C%20CEO%20of%20digital%20marketing%20firm%20ASY%20Digital.%20%26quot%3BEverything%20is%20ready%20from%20our%20side.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Yavuz%20and%20his%20counterparts%2C%20there's%20serious%20appeal%20in%20having%20another%20ad-supported%20app%20inside%20Meta's%20ad%20manager.%20And%20that%20could%20be%20trouble%20for%20Twitter.%20Meta's%20ad%20platform%20centralizes%20buying%20across%20its%20properties%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Instagram%20and%20Facebook%20%E2%80%94%20and%20is%20extremely%20effective%2C%20using%20advanced%20targeting%20and%20optimization%20to%20deliver%20better%20performance%20than%20other%20digital%20media%20outlets%2C%20with%20the%20possible%20exception%20of%20Google.%20Once%20Meta%20adds%20a%20check%20box%20to%20extend%20ads%20to%20Threads%2C%20ad%20buyers%20will%20check%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20number%20one%20platform%20for%20pretty%20much%20all%20the%20brands%20we%20work%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Carly%20London%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20growth%20marketing%20agency%20Sometimes%20Curly%2C%20of%20Meta.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we're%20able%20to%20use%20the%20power%20of%20that%20advertising%2C%20to%20expand%20to%20a%20Twitter-like%20audience%2C%20that%20can%20be%20huge.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAmong%20the%20nearly%20all%20marketers%20we%20spoke%20with%2C%20the%20prevailing%20sentiment%20was%20overwhelming%20trust%20in%20Meta's%20ad%20platform%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20for%20sure%20start%20to%20test%20immediately%20because%20it's%20Meta.%20Generally%20trust%20them%20in%20every%20placement%20they%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20David%20Herrmann%2C%20CEO%20of%20ad%20agency%20Herrmann%20Digital.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20always%20making%20updates%20to%20improve%20targeting%20and%20placements%20and%20ad%20optimization%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Carl%20Bivona%20sr.%20director%20of%20social%20media%20at%20Ignite%20Visibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20already%20have%20better%20ad%20technology%20from%20a%20marketer's%20perspective%20than%20Twitter.%20Facebook's%20ads%2C%20technology%2C%20and%20interfaces%20are%20much%20better%20than%20Twitter's%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Trevor%20Dudeck%2C%20CEO%20of%20ad%20agency%20Lemonade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe'll%20be%20ready%20to%20jump%20in%20as%20soon%20as%20Meta%20rolls%20out%20advertising%20on%20Threads%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Josh%20Keller%2C%20CEO%20of%20Union%20Square%20Media.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20communicating%20with%20them%20currently%20about%20the%20launch.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20enthusiasm%20from%20advertisers%20has%20little%20to%20do%20with%20content%20moderation%20or%20the%20culture%20war%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20the%20marketers%20we%20spoke%20with%20brought%20up%20Elon%20Musk's%20or%20Zuckerberg's%20politics%2C%20just%20as%20few%20marketers%20slowed%20their%20spending%20amid%20Meta's%20various%20scandals%20last%20decade.%20Marketers%20want%20performance%2C%20and%20Meta%20delivers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20number%20one%20goal%20is%20what%20will%20make%20the%20company%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20London.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20get%20involved%20in%20any%20other%20kind%20of%20issues%2C%20or%20Twitter%20versus%20this%20or%20versus%20that.%20I%20don't%20really%20care.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Meta%2C%20there's%20risk%20that%20Threads%20cannibalizes%20Instagram's%20revenue%20over%20Twitter's.%20Meta%2C%20after%20all%2C%20built%20Threads%20on%20top%20of%20Instagram's%20network%2C%20and%20advertisers%20want%20more%20than%20just%20a%20novel%20way%20to%20reach%20the%20same%20people.%20%26quot%3BIf%20it's%20just%20the%20same%20thing%20as%20Instagram%2C%20that's%20not%20going%20to%20be%20as%20enticing%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20executive%20at%20a%20major%20digital%20advertising%20agency.%20%26quot%3BThreads%20likely%20needs%20to%20pull%20in%20some%20growth%20from%20outside%20the%20Instagram%