s%20%26quot%3Bburning%26quot%3B%20since%20the%20last%2085%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20people%20have%20now%20become%20aware%20and%20will%20fight%20%26quot%3Bthis%20kind%20of%20politics%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Parliament%20session%20is%20going%20on%20and%20instead%20of%20speaking%20on%20the%20floor%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20making%20speeches%20here%20and%20there%20and%20by%20doing%20so%20he%20is%20tarnishing%20democracy%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kharge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20misdeeds%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20cannot%20be%20erased%20by%20calling%20names%20to%20the%20opposition%20parties%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kharge%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20chief%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20BJP%20for%20not%20allowing%20him%20to%20speak%20inside%20Parliament%20and%20for%20jeering%20at%20opposition%20members%20for%20wearing%20black%20clothes%20as%20a%20mark%20of%20protest%20for%20not%20allowing%20them%20to%20raised%20the%20Manipur%20issue%20in%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnly%20those%20having%20a%20mindset%20against%20Dalits%2C%20tribals%20and%20backward%20people%20can%20make%20fun%20of%20black%20clothes%2C%20but%20for%20us%20black%20is%20a%20symbol%20of%20protest%20and%20strength.%20Black%20colour%20is%20a%20symbol%20of%20justice%20and%20a%20symbol%20of%20dignity.%20The%20people%20of%20Manipur%20deserve%20justice%2C%20peace%20and%20respect%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20tweet%20in%20Hindi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kharge%20said%20the%20BJP%20cannot%20run%20away%20from%20its%20responsibility%20by%20plunging%20the%20life%20of%20Manipur%20into%20%26quot%3Bblack%20darkness%26quot%3B%2C%20by%20adopting%20a%20%26quot%3Bdictatorial%20attitude%26quot%3B%20and%20by%20diverting%20the%20attention%20from%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20has%20never%20been%20a%20darker%20period%20in%20the%20history%20of%20Parliament%20than%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20people%20have%20become%20aware%20and%20they%20will%20fight%20and%20continue%20to%20do%20so...This%20means%20you%20do%20not%20want%20to%20talk%20in%20Parliament%20-%20the%20temple%20of%20democracy%2C%20and%20want%20to%20give%20a%20political%20speech%20in%20Rajasthan%20while%20opening%20new%20medical%20colleges%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kharge%20told%20reporters%20outside%20Parliament%2C%20while%20attacking%20the%20prime%20minister%20for%20not%20speaking%20in%20Parliament%20on%20the%20Manipur%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20burning%20of%20Manipur%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bblack%20chapter%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20which%20did%20not%20take%20care%20of%20the%20crying%20people%20of%20Manipur%20in%20the%20last%2085%20days%20that%20%26quot%3Bgovernment%20is%20a%20blot%20on%20humanity%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20has%20been%20accusing%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20not%20making%20a%20statement%20in%20Parliament%20on%20the%20northeastern%20state%2C%20which%20has%20seen%20violence%20since%20May%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Houses%20of%20Parliament%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20transact%20any%20business%20amid%20the%20uproar%20caused%20by%20the%20opposition%2C%20demanding%20a%20statement%20from%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20a%20discussion%20on%20Manipur%20thereafter.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690447260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fin9f7gr8_mallikarjun-kharge-ani_625x300_27_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-not-speaking-in-parliament-but-busy-talking-in-rallies-congress-chief-mallikarjun-kharge-4244611%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kha