nald%20Trump's%20presidential%20campaign%20in%202016.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20came%20to%20light%20in%202018%20after%20it%20was%20revealed%20that%20Cambridge%20Analytica%20had%20paid%20Facebook%20app%20developers%20to%20get%20access%20to%20nearly%2087%20million%20users%20on%20the%20social%20media%20platform.%20The%20data%20was%20used%20by%20the%20company%20for%20a%20targeted%20campaign%20in%20the%20election%20run-up%20that%20saw%20Trump%20taking%20over%20as%20the%2045th%20President%20of%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20still%20not%20clear%20how%20much%20amount%20an%20individual%20user%20will%20get%20as%20part%20of%20the%20settlement.%20The%20larger%20the%20pool%20of%20claimants%2C%20the%20smaller%20the%20settlement%20amount%20will%20be%20for%20every%20individual%2C%20given%20that%20the%20total%20money%20will%20be%20divided%20among%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20not%20been%20the%20only%20instance%20of%20Meta%20violating%20data%20privacy%20rules.%20In%20May%20this%20year%2C%20the%20social%20media%20company%20was%20directed%20to%20pay%20%241.3%20billion%20in%20settlement%20for%20violating%20European%20Union%20data%20protection%20rules.%20The%20company%20was%20also%20asked%20to%20stop%20the%20transfer%20of%20data%20collected%20from%20Facebook%20users%20in%20Europe%20to%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ftechnology%2F2023%2Fmay%2F22%2Ffacebook-fined-mishandling-user-information-ireland-eu-meta%5C%22%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20fine%20was%20imposed%20by%20Ireland's%20Data%20Protection%20Commission%20(DPC)%20after%20a%20legal%20challenge%20by%20Austrian%20privacy%20campaigner%20Max%20Scherms%20after%20Edward%20Snowden's%20claim%20that%20European%20users'%20data%20is%20not%20sufficiently%20protected%20from%20US%20intelligence%20agencies%20when%20it%20is%20transferred%20across%20the%20Atlantic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20applied%20to%20data%20collected%20by%20only%20Facebook%20and%20no%20other%20Meta%20owned%20platforms%20like%20WhatsApp%2C%20and%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690446420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Flj6r0ijo_facebook-generic_625x300_17_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-facebook-users-can-apply-for-their-share-of-725-million-privacy-settlement-till-august-25-4244426%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Facebook%20users%20in%20the%20US%20can%20apply%20for%20their%20share%20of%20a%20%24%20725%20million%20privacy%20settlement%20that%20the%20social%20media%20platform's%20parent%20company%20Meta%20agreed%20to%20pay%20last%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-facebook-users-can-apply-for-their-share-of-725-million-privacy-settlement-till-august-25-4244426%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-facebook-users-can-apply-for-their-share-of-725-million-privacy-settlement-till-august-25-4244426%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-facebook-users-can-apply-for-their-share-of-725-million-privacy-settlement-till-august-25-4244426%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kuwait%20hangs%20five%2C%20including%202015%20mosque%20bombing%20convict%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690446381000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102166459%2Cimgsize-293304.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fkuwait-hangs-five-including-2015-mosque-bombing-convict%2Farticleshow%2F102166526.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102166526.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EKuwait%20executed%20five%20people%2C%20including%20o