bjected%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3EOppenhemier%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20producers%20have%20already%20blacked%20out%20scenes%20in%20the%20film%20which%20are%20remotely%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flink.sbstck.com%2Fredirect%2F4161d7d9-b237-4a9d-ac27-b2921e8510dd%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Flink.sbstck.com%2Fredirect%2F4161d7d9-b237-4a9d-ac27-b2921e8510dd%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1690515638109000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1z1OBB-OnDbNH1VQBIkTy_%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enude%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20%E2%80%98sexual%E2%80%99%20to%20secure%20a%20release%20here.%20Our%20own%20censors%20have%20added%20that%20ridiculous%20disclaimer%20about%20smoking.%20Plus%2C%20our%20government%20is%20actively%20considering%20censoring%20films%20and%20shows%20on%20OTT%20platforms%20of%20%E2%80%98vulgar%E2%80%99%20content.%20Why%20this%20prudishness%2C%20at%20a%20time%20when%20everyone%20has%20access%20to%20all%20kinds%20of%20stuff%20on%20the%20Internet%3F%20Unless%20there%20is%20a%20plan%20to%20censor%20that%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20Oppenheimer%20had%20studied%20Sanskrit%20and%20had%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flink.sbstck.com%2Fredirect%2Fc199bbed-4d84-4895-8391-483e148bd610%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Flink.sbstck.com%2Fredirect%2Fc199bbed-4d84-4895-8391-483e148bd610%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1690515638109000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1_UlSMU4gYBH-fnb17RD7Y%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0read%20the%20Gita%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0deeply%20is%20well%20documented.%20One%20would%20have%20thought%20that%20the%20Hindutva%20types%2C%20who%20never%20resist%20an%20opportunity%20to%20proclaim%20from%20the%20rooftops%20that%20India%20(i.e.%2C%20Hindu%20India)%20was%20superior%20to%20all%20other%20religions%2C%20would%20have%20been%20overjoyed%20at%20this.%20Add%20to%20that%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20invented%20the%20atom%20bomb%20(though%20it%20was%20first%20made%20in%20India%20several%20centuries%20ago)%2C%20a%20destructive%20device%2C%20would%20have%20fed%20right%20into%20their%20masculinist%20and%20militaristic%20fantasies.%20They%20would%20have%20then%20rushed%20to%20see%20the%20film%20in%20large%20numbers.%20Instead%2C%20they%20are%20carping%20about%20the%20use%20of%20the%20Gita%20in%20a%20sex%20scene%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20interested%20in%20good%20cinema%20are%20heading%20to%20theatres%20to%20see%20this%20film%20and%20coming%20back%20impressed%20%E2%80%94%20at%20the%20scale%2C%20the%20story%20and%20most%20of%20all%2C%20the%20lessons%20the%20film%20holds.%20That%20the%20father%20of%20the%20most%20destructive%20weapon%20created%20till%20then%2C%20which%20killed%20lakhs%20of%20Japanese%2C%20is%20filled%20with%20doubt%20about%20his%20invention.%20Nuclear%20devices%20were%20supposed%20to%20create%20peace%20for%20all%20time%20%E2%80%94%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%2C%20as%20we%20have%20seen%20in%20the%20war-filled%20decades%20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOppenheimer%E2%80%99s%20self-doubts%20turned%20him%20into%20an%20object%20of%20suspicion%20in%20the%20American%20security%20establishment.%20He%20was%20suspected%20of%20being%20a%20communist%2C%20the%20worst%20crime%20in%20their%20eyes%20in%20the%20years%20just%20before%20the%20Cold%20War%20began%20%E2%80%94%20the%20FBI%20kept%20tabs%20on%20him%20and%20his%20top%20security%20Q%20clearance%20as%20the%20man%20working%20on%20the%20bomb%20was%20revoked%20in%201954%3B%20the%20decision%20was%20nullified%20only%20in%202022%2C%20long%20after%20he%20had%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20so-ca