ot%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20has%20a%20scene%20in%20which%20a%20bunch%20of%20policemen%20attend%20a%20gender%20sensitivity%20training%20programme.%20A%20few%20of%20them%20make%20snide%20remarks%20as%20the%20session%20is%20introduced.%20Their%20laidback%20attitude%20instantly%20reveals%20why%20the%20town%20has%20seen%20a%20spate%20of%20crimes%20against%20women.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20show%20also%20factors%20in%20domestic%20violence%2C%20homophobia%2C%20unsafe%20abortions%2C%20female%20infanticide%2C%20cybercrime%2C%20jilted%20lovers%2C%20depredations%20of%20corrupt%20and%20cynical%20politicians%20and%20flawed%20policing%20while%20it%20depicts%20a%20probe%20into%20the%20circumstances%20in%20which%20a%20college%20girl%20is%20attacked%20with%20acid.%20A%20case%20of%20biting%20off%20too%20much%3F%20May%20be.%20The%20writing%20is%20strong%20enough%20to%20keep%20matters%20in%20check.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20story%2C%20primarily%20centred%20on%20the%20investigation%2C%20unfolds%20at%20a%20deliberate%20pace%20while%20the%20victim%20lies%20near-comatose%20in%20a%20hospital%20with%20severe%20burns%20on%20her%20face%20and%20parts%20of%20her%20upper%20body.%20The%20male%20protagonist's%20negotiations%20with%20the%20demons%20of%20his%20own%20mind%20and%20the%20entanglements%20that%20he%20gets%20into%20in%20the%20workplace%20and%20at%20home%20constitute%20another%20large%20chunk%20of%20the%20narrative.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijay%20Varma%2C%20in%20a%20garb%20that%20allows%20no%20room%20for%20heroic%20showboating%2C%20leads%20the%20charge%20in%20a%20measured%20and%20highly%20effective%20manner%20to%20prop%20up%20a%20reasonably%20absorbing%2C%20if%20a%20touch%20ponderous%2C%20show%20that%20leans%20heavily%20on%20the%20actor%20getting%20the%20nuances%20of%20the%20role%20right.%20That%20he%20does%20that%20-%20and%20a%20little%20more%20-%20is%20half%20the%20battle%20won%20for%20a%20series%20that%20is%20mindful%20of%20the%20necessity%20to%20be%20on%20point%20with%20its%20messaging.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lead%20actor%20is%20ably%20supported%20by%20Shweta%20Tripathi%20Sharma%20(who%20spends%20a%20large%20part%20of%20the%20series%20in%20a%20supine%20and%20silent%20state)%2C%20Seema%20Biswas%2C%20Yashpal%20Sharma%20and%20Gopal%20Datt%2C%20all%20perfectly%20in%20sync%20with%20the%20realistic%20drift%20of%20the%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20screenplay%20by%20Sumit%20Saxena%2C%20Arunabh%20Kumar%20and%20Karan%20Singh%20Tyagi%20does%20not%20come%20up%20with%20big%20surprises%20and%20hard-hitting%20blows%2C%20but%20it%20does%20foray%2C%20directly%20and%20indirectly%2C%20into%20essential%20themes%20that%20subtly%20bring%20out%20the%20hero's%20struggle%20not%20to%20let%20an%20environment%20steeped%20in%20misogyny%20get%20to%20him%20and%20change%20the%20way%20he%20views%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20interesting%20aspects%20of%20%3Cem%3EKaalkoot%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20is%20the%20music.%20Both%20the%20background%20score%20and%20the%20songs%2C%20composed%20by%20Raghav-Arjun%2C%20lend%20the%20show%20an%20earthy%2C%20rooted%20feel%20that%20serves%20to%20heighten%20its%20relatability%20quotient%20even%20as%20it%20explores%20the%20darkness%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20town.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20strand%20of%20the%20story%20centres%20on%20a%20woman%20(Suzanna%20Mukherjee)%20who%20SI%20Tripathi%20and%20his%20mother%20-%20especially%20the%20latter%20-%20grow%20close%20to.%20Marriage%20is%20on%20the%20cards%20between%20her%20and%20the%20ever-sceptical%20policeman.%20But%20as%20things%20pan%20out%2C%20the%20relationship%20hits%20hurdles%20that%20force%20the%20cop%20to%20take%20another%20hard%20look%20at%20himself%20in%20the%20mirror.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijay%20Varma%20dons%20a%20guise%20that%20is%20the%20exact%20opposite%20of%20the%20psychopath%20he%20played%20in%20Dahaad.%20He%20takes%20effortlessly%20to%20the%20angularities%20of%20the%20doubt-ridden%20policeman%20who%20must%20deal%20with%20a%20range%20of%20prickly%20issues%20in%20his%20quest%20for%20the%20truth%20about%20the%20acid%20attack%20-%20and%20himself.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hero%20isn't%20a%20brash%2C%20bad-tempered%20Bollywood-style%20man%20in%20uniform.%20He%20is%20tentative%2C%20soft-spoken%2C%20anything%20but%20trigger%20happy%2C%20even%20a%20mamma's%20boy%20and%20a%20guy%20who%20bathes%20in%20warm%20water.%20You've%20got%20to%20be%20more%20virile%2C%20his%20superior%20quips.%20The%20younger%20cop%20has%20no%20riposte%20because%20he%20probably%20does%20not%20feel%20the%20need%20for%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FxyGNai2fFg8%3Fsi%3D5VH2NfgOKhLmSY9B%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20character%20is%20believable%20and%20beset%20with%20contradictions%20that%2C%20at%20crucial%20junctures%2C%20stop%20him%20in%20his%20tracks.%20He%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20cop%20you%20might%20root%20for%20in%20a%20crunch%20situation%20even%20if%20you%20are%20not%20completely%20convinced%20that%20he%20has%20the%20chops%20to%20be%20the%20last%20man%20standing.%20His%20honesty%20shines%20through%20and%20yet%20his%20conduct%20-%20as%20also%20that%20of%20his%20colleagues%20-%20raises%20questions%20without%20delivering%20answers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESub-inspector%20Ravi%20Shankar%20Tripathi%2C%20just%20three%20months%20and%20a%20bit%20into%20his%20job%20and%20still%20at%20odds%20with%20its%20requirements%2C%20is%20one%20of%20three%20key%20personnel%20in%20the%20Sarsi%20police%20station%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20MacMohan%20Ganj.%20The%20location%20is%20fictional%20but%20the%20plight%20of%20the%20protagonist%20and%20the%20stories%20that%20he%20confronts%20in%20the%20course%20of%20the%20investigation%20are%20firmly%20rooted%20in%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESI%20Tripathi%2C%20son%20of%20an%20anti-establishment%20Hindi%20professor-poet%20who%20is%20no%20more%2C%20has%20to%20contend%20with%20a%20cynical%20and%20hard-to-please%20boss%2C%20SHO%20Jagdish%20Sahay%20(Gopal%20Datt)%2C%20who%20never%20loses%20an%20opportunity%20to%20run%20him%20down%2C%20and%20a%20well-meaning%20mother%20(Seema%20Biswas)%2C%20who%20will%20not%20pause%20until%20she%20has%20found%20a%20bride%20for%20him.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavi's%20mother%20is%20in%20possession%20of%20a%20photograph%20of%20a%20girl%20(presumably%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20long%20series%20of%20snaps%20that%20she%20has%20shown%20her%20son%20since%20he%20has%20landed%20a%20job)%20she%20wants%20a%20disinterested%20Ravi%20to%20marry.%20It%20turns%20out%20that%20this%20very%20girl%20is%20the%20one%20who%20has%20had%20acid%20thrown%20at%20her.%20The%20case%20is%20assigned%20to%20Ravi.%20His%20life%20from%20this%20point%20on%20gets%20inextricably%20intertwined%20with%20Parul's%20fate%20and%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20investigation.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim%2C%20Parul%20Chaturvedi%20(Shweta%20Tripathi%20Sharma)%2C%20is%20hospitalised%20with%20serious%20facial%20injuries.%20She%20is%20unable%20to%20talk.%20It%20is%20her%20parents%2C%20a%20younger%20sibling%2C%20sundry%20college%20mates%20and%20other%20friends%20who%20are%20on%20the%20investigator's%20radar%20who%20provide%20the%20information%20and%20insights%20that%20could%20help%20the%20cops%20solve%20the%20case.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESI%20Tripathi's%20investigation%20-%20an%20exercise%20in%20which%20his%20aide%20is%20Constable%20Sattu%20Yadav%20(Yashpal%20Sharma)%2C%20a%20somewhat%20jaded%20cop%20who%20sways%20between%20cockiness%20and%20confusion%20-%20leads%20him%20to%20a%20variety%20of%20suspects%20and%20putative%20witnesses.%20But%20most%20of%20the%20trails%20go%20cold.%20Yadavji%20shadows%20Ravi%20wherever%20the%20latter%20goes%20in%20the%20line%20of%20duty%20-%20the%20man%20is%20both%20a%20helpful%20co-worker%20and%20a%20troublesome%20mole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20%3Cem%3EKaalkoot%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20comes%20close%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20two%20investigative%20thrillers%20(Amazon%20Prime%20Video's%20%3Cem%3EDahaad%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%20and%20Netflix's%20%3Cem%3EKohrra%3C%2Fem%3E)%20that%20have%20raised%20the%20bar%20for%20the%20genre%2C%20a%20comparative%20assessment%20is%20inevitable%2C%20if%20odious.%3Cem%3E%20Kaalkoot%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eisn't%20in%20the%20same%20league%2C%20but%20the%20fact%20that%20one%20is%20able%20to%20mention%20it%20alongside%20the%20earlier%20two%20shows%20should%20itself%20be%20taken%20as%20an%20accolade.%20The%20series%20deserves%20its%20share%20of%20praise%20for%20giving%20the%20genre%20a%20veneer%20of%20freshness.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690444740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F17628jno_vijay-_625x300_27_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fkaalkoot-review-vijay-varma-leads-the-charge-in-understated-police-procedural-2-5-stars-4244538%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kaalkoot%20Review%3A%20The%20lead%20actor%20is%20ably%20supported%20by%20Shweta%20Tripathi%20Sharma%2C%20Seema%20Biswas%2C%20Yashpal%20Sharma%20and%20Gopal%20Datt%2C%20all%20perfectly%20in%20sync%20with%20the%20realistic%20drift%20of%20the%20story.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fkaalkoot-review-vijay-varma-leads-the-charge-in-understated-police-procedural-2-5-stars-4244538%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fkaalkoot-review-vijay-varma-leads-the-charge-in-understated-police-procedural-2-5-stars-4244538%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%