d%20after%20a%20major%20fire%20broke%20out%20on%20a%20cargo%20vessel%20carrying%20nearly%203%2C000%20cars%20off%20the%20Netherlands%20coast.%20An%20electric%20vehicle%2C%20one%20of%2025%20on%20board%2C%20is%20suspected%20to%20have%20caused%20the%20fire.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fire%20broke%20out%20on%20Tuesday%20night%20on%20an%2018%2C500-tonne%20Panama-registered%20vessel%2C%20the%20Fremantle%20Highway%2C%20which%20was%20en%20route%20from%20Germany%20to%20Egypt.%20Crew%20members%20tried%20to%20douse%20the%20blaze%20and%20some%20were%20forced%20to%20jump%20overboard%20when%20their%20efforts%20were%20unsuccessful%2C%20said%20a%20report%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConfirming%20the%20death%20of%20an%20Indian%20crew%20member%2C%20the%20Indian%20Embassy%20in%20the%20Netherlands%20tweeted%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20deeply%20saddened%20by%20the%20incident%20involving%20Ship%20'Fremantle%20Highway'%20in%20North%20Sea%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20death%20of%20an%20Indian%20seafarer%20%26amp%3B%20injuries%20to%20the%20crew.%20Embassy%20of%20India%20is%20in%20touch%20with%20family%20of%20the%20deceased%20%26amp%3B%20is%20assisting%20in%20repatriation%20of%20the%20mortal%20remains.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EEmbassy%20is%20also%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20remaining%2020%20injured%20crew%20members%2C%20who%20are%20safe%20and%20receiving%20medical%20attention.%20All%20possible%20assistance%20is%20being%20extended%20in%20coordination%20with%20the%20Dutch%20authorities%20and%20the%20shipping%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMEAIndia%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40MEAIndia%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20IndiainNetherlands%20(%40IndinNederlands)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIndinNederlands%2Fstatus%2F1684221629642031108%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2026%2C%202023%3