%20PTI%20report%20said%20a%20distress%20call%20came%20when%20the%20ship%20was%20about%2030%20km%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Ameland.%20The%2023%20crew%20members%20attempted%20to%20put%20out%20the%20fire%20themselves%2C%20but%20the%20blaze%20spread%20too%20fast.%20Dutch%20news%20outlets%20reported%20that%20specialised%20firefighters%20were%20brought%20in%20from%20Rotterdam%2C%20but%20the%20situation%20had%20already%20become%20too%20dangerous%20by%20the%20time%20they%20arrived.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeven%20of%20the%20crew%20jumped%20into%20the%20sea%20and%20were%20picked%20up%20by%20nearby%20ships.%20The%20remaining%20crew%20members%20were%20rescued%20by%20helicopters.%20It%20is%20not%20clear%20how%20the%20person%20who%20died%20was%20killed%2C%20the%20reports%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20authorities%20are%20now%20focusing%20their%20efforts%20on%20preventing%20the%20listing%20ship%20from%20sinking.%20A%20tugboat%20was%20able%20to%20attach%20a%20rope%20to%20the%20Fremantle%20Highway%20and%20prevent%20it%20from%20drifting%20into%20shipping%20lanes.%20Other%20boats%20are%20on%20standby%20to%20try%20to%20help%20pull%20the%20vessel%20to%20safety%2C%20said%20the%20PTI%20report.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690444080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fank2moa8_dutch-coast-ship-fire-reuters_625x300_27_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findian-killed-as-ship-catches-fire-off-dutch-coast-ev-may-have-been-cause-4244488%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20Indian%20crew%20member%20was%20killed%20and%2020%20others%20were%20injured%20after%20a%20major%20fire%20broke%20out%20on%20a%20cargo%20vessel%20carrying%20nearly%203%2C000%20cars%20off%20the%20Netherlands%20coast.%20An%20electric%20vehicle%2C%20one%20of%2025%20on%20board%2C%20is%20suspected%20to%20have%20caused%20the%20fire.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia