erbate%20global%20food%20price%20inflation%20and%20should%20be%20reversed%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Standard%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-s-rice-restrictions-could-fuel-food-price-inflation-imf-economist-123072500863_1.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGourinchas%2C%20while%20addressing%20a%20news%20conference%2C%20said%20that%20the%20move%20would%20have%20a%20similar%20effect%20to%20the%20suspension%20of%20Ukraine%20Black%20Sea%20grain%20export%20deal%20and%20drive%20up%20grain%20prices%20in%20other%20countries%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20could%20rise%20by%2010-15%25%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20current%20environment%2C%20these%20types%20of%20restrictions%20are%20likely%20to%20exacerbate%20volatility%20on%20food%20prices%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%2C%20and%20they%20can%20also%20lead%20to%20retaliatory%20measures.%20We%20would%20encourage%20the%20removal%20of%20these%20types%20of%20export%20restrictions%20because%20they%20can%20be%20harmful%20globally%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Standard%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20Gourinchas%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20had%20banned%20the%20export%20of%20non-basmati%20rice%20last%20week%20owing%20to%20fears%20of%20a%20domestic%20shortage%20after%20late%20monsoon%20rains%20hurt%20paddy%20crops%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fhow-to%2Fwhy-indian-rice-export-ban-is-so-important-to-global-trade%2Farticleshow%2F102015630.cms%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2020%2C%20the%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifpri.org%2Fblog%2Findias-new-ban-rice-exports-potential-threats-global-supply-prices-and-food-security%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20would%20restrict%20exports%20of%20non-basmati%20rice%20to%20calm%20domestic%20rice%20prices%20that%20had%20risen%20more%20than