nd%20is%20assisting%20in%20the%20repatriation%20of%20the%20mortal%20remains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEmbassy%20is%20also%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20remaining%2020%20injured%20crew%20members%2C%20who%20are%20safe%20and%20receiving%20medical%20attention.%20All%20possible%20assistance%20is%20being%20extended%20in%20coordination%20with%20the%20Dutch%20authorities%20and%20the%20shipping%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERescue%20boats%20and%20helicopters%20were%20used%20to%20get%20the%2023%20crew%20members%20off%20the%20ship%20after%20some%20had%20jumped%20in%20the%20water%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Dutch%20coastguard%20told%20CNN%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPictures%20show%20grey%20smoke%20emitting%20from%20the%20ship%20amid%20fears%20the%20vessel%20could%20sink%2027%20kilometers%20north%20of%20the%20Dutch%20island%2C%20Ameland%2C%20off%20the%20Wadden%20Sea%20%E2%80%93%20a%20UNESCO%20World%20Heritage%20Site%20that%20is%20considered%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20regions%20for%20migratory%20birds%20in%20the%20world%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fire%20may%20have%20been%20started%20by%20one%20of%20the%2025%20electric%20cars%20on%20board%2C%20according%20to%20Dutch%20national%20broadcaster%20NOS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDutch%20firefighters%20were%20still%20struggling%20to%20put%20out%20the%20fire%20on%20the%20cargo%20ship%20some%2016%20hours%20after%20the%20blaze%20started%2C%20a%20Dutch%20coastguard%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20could%20take%20hours%2C%20days%2C%20or%20even%20weeks%20to%20make%20sure%20the%20fire%20is%20completely%20out%2C%20a%20spokesman%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20is%20currently%20too%20dangerous%20to%20put%20firefighters%20on%20the%20ship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20start%20filling%20the%20ship%20with%20water%2C%20you%20risk%20destabilising%20it%20and%20that%20could%20tip%20it%20over%2C%E2%80%9D%20spokesman%20Edwin%20Grammeman%20told%20NOS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%