href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblogs.microsoft.com%2Fon-the-issues%2F2023%2F07%2F26%2Fanthropic-google-microsoft-openai-launch-frontier-model-forum%2F%5C%22%3Eblog%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20body%2C%20called%20the%20Frontier%20Model%20Forum%2C%20is%20going%20to%20draw%20on%20the%20technical%20and%20operational%20expertise%20of%20its%20member%20companies%20to%20benefit%20the%20entire%20AI%20ecosystem.%20The%20group%20will%20focus%20on%20technical%20evaluations%20and%20will%20set%20benchmarks.%20It%20will%20also%20develop%20a%20public%20library%20of%20solutions%20to%20support%20best%20practices%20and%20standards%20in%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20blog%20notes%3A%20%E2%80%9CGovernments%20and%20industry%20agree%20that%2C%20while%20AI%20offers%20tremendous%20promise%20to%20benefit%20the%20world%2C%20appropriate%20guardrails%20are%20required%20to%20mitigate%20risks.%20Important%20contributions%20to%20these%20efforts%20have%20already%20been%20made%20by%20the%20US%20and%20UK%20governments%2C%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20the%20OECD%2C%20the%20G7%20(via%20the%20Hiroshima%20AI%20process)%2C%20and%20others.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20body%20that%20primarily%20focuses%20on%20mitigating%20AI%E2%80%99s%20risks%2C%20the%20Frontier%20Model%20Forum%20will%20be%20open%20for%20membership%20to%20organisations%20that%20develop%20and%20deploy%20frontier%20AI%20models%2C%20demonstrate%20commitment%20to%20safety%20and%20wish%20to%20participate%20in%20join%20initiatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Forum%20will%20establish%20an%20advisory%20board%20in%20the%20coming%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20goals%20of%20this%20body%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20Advancing%20AI%20safety%20research%20to%20promote%20responsible%20development%20of%20frontier%20models.%20According%20to%20Microsoft%E2%80%99s%20statement%2C%20it%20will%20also%20try%20to%20minimise%20risks%2C%20and%20enable%20independent%20and%20standardised%20evaluations%20of%20capabilities%20and%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20Identifying%20best%20practices%20for%20the%20responsible%20development%20and%20deployment%20of%20frontier%20models.%20The%20body%20will%20attempt%20to%20help%20the%20public%20understand%20the%20nature%2C%20capabilities%2C%20limitations%2C%20and%20impact%20of%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20Collaborating%20with%20policymakers%2C%20academics%2C%20civil%20society%2C%20and%20companies%20to%20share%20knowledge%20about%20trust%20and%20safety%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20Supporting%20efforts%20to%20develop%20applications%20that%20can%20help%20meet%20society%E2%80%99s%20challenges%2C%20%E2%80%9Csuch%20as%20climate%20change%20mitigation%20and%20adaptation%2C%20early%20cancer%20detection%20and%20prevention%2C%20and%20combating%20cyber%20threats.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690439728000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F06142516%2FUntitled-design-19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fopenai-google-and-other-ai-leaders-set-up-industry-watchdog-to-ensure-safety%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20Microsoft's%20blog%2C%20the%20body%2C%20called%20the%20Frontier%20Model%20Forum%2C%20is%20going%20to%20draw%20on%20the%20technical%20and%20operational%20expertise%20of%20its%20member%20companies%20to%20benefit%20the%20entire%20AI%20ecosystem.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fopenai-google-and-other-ai-leaders-set-up-industry-watchdog-to-ensure-safety%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Niger%3A%20Soldiers%20Claim%20To%20Have%20Overthrown%20President%20Bazoum%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26232726%2FScreenshot-2023-07-26-at-11.26.56-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ENiger%E2%80%99s%20President%20Mohamed%20Bazoum%20has%20been%20removed%20from%20power%2C%20according%20to%20repor