dings%20Is%20Not%20Violation%20Of%20Copyright%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20government%20has%20issued%20a%20directive%20stating%20that%20playing%20Bollywood%20songs%20at%20wedding%20ceremonies%20and%20other%20festivities%20will%20not%20result%20in%20legal%20action%20for%20copyright%20infringement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20directive%20was%20issued%20in%20response%20to%20numerous%20complaints%20regarding%20the%20collection%20of%20royalties%20by%20copyright%20societies%20for%20the%20performance%20of%20Hindi%20film%20songs%20at%20wedding%20functions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20public%20notice%2C%20the%20Department%20for%20Promotion%2C%20Industry%2C%20and%20Internal%20Trade%20(DPIIT)%20said%20that%20it%20has%20received%20several%20complaints%20and%20grievances%20from%20the%20general%20public%20and%20other%20stakeholders%20about%20the%20alleged%20collection%20of%20royalties%20by%20the%20Copyright%20Societies%20for%20the%20performance%20of%20musical%20works%20in%20marriage%20functions%20in%20contravention%20of%20the%20letter%20and%20spirit%20of%20Section%2052%20(1)%20(za)%20of%20the%20Copyright%20Act%201957.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESection%2052%20of%20the%20act%20deals%20with%20certain%20acts%20that%20would%20not%20constitute%20an%20infringement%20of%20Copyright.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20Section%2052%20(1)%20(za)%20specifically%20mentions%20the%20performance%20of%20literary%2C%20dramatic%2C%20or%20musical%20work%20or%20of%20a%20sound%20recording%20in%20the%20course%20of%20any%20bona%20fide%20religious%20ceremony%20or%20an%20official%20ceremony%20as%20not%20constituting%20infringement%20of%20copyright.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReligious%20ceremonies%20include%20a%20marriage%20procession%20and%20other%20social%20festivities%20associated%20with%20marriage%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20view%20of%20this%2C%20%26quot%3BCopyright%20Societies%20are%20directed%20to%20strictly%20refrain%20from%20entering%20into%20acts%20that%20are%20in%20contravention%20of%20Section%2052%20(1)%20(za)%20%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20act%20%26quot%3Bin%20order%20to%20avoid%20any%20legal%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20DPIIT%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20cautioned%20the%20general%20public%20not%20to%20accede%20to%20any%20uncalled%20demands%20from%20any%20individual%2C%20organisation%2C%20or%20copyright%20society%20that%20are%20in%20violation%20of%20this%20section.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20is%20welcomed%20by%20the%20general%20public%20and%20the%20hospitality%20sector%2C%20which%20took%20the%20brunt%20of%20the%20pressure%20from%20various%20copyright%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20inputs%20from%20PTI)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690439340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-05%2Fpkntgke_shaadi-ka-video-_625x300_19_May_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-says-playing-film-songs-at-weddings-is-not-violation-of-copyright-4244215%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20decision%20is%20welcomed%20by%20the%20general%20public%20and%20the%20hospitality%20sector%2C%20which%20took%20the%20brunt%20of%20the%20pressure%20from%20various%20copyright%20organisations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-says-playing-film-songs-at-weddings-is-not-violation-of-copyright-4244215%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-says-playing-film-songs-at-weddings-is-not-violation-of-copyright-4244215%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-says-playing-film-songs-at-weddings-is-not-violation-of-copyright-4244215%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Irked%20Rohit%20dismisses%20concern%20over%20Kohli's%20overseas%20Test%20form%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690439124000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2