0pick%20her%20up.%20%E2%80%9CHer%20coaching%20started%20at%205%20am%20and%20ended%20at%208%3A15%20am%3B%20I%20used%20to%20drop%20her%20off%20and%20pick%20her%20up%20from%20the%20coaching%2C%20but%20that%20was%20the%20day%20when%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20go%20to%20pick%20her%20up%2C%20and%20since%20then%2C%20she%20is%20missing.%20I%20curse%20myself%20for%20not%20going%20to%20pick%20my%20daughter%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20disappearance%20occurred%20right%20after%20the%20reopening%20of%20schools%2Fcoaching%20centres%20in%20Manipur%2C%20which%20had%20been%20closed%20because%20of%20ethnic%20violence.%20Luwangbi%20attended%20her%20classes%2C%20and%20CCTV%20footage%20showed%20her%20riding%20a%20KTM%20Duke%20200%20with%20Phijam%20Hemanjit%20Singh%2C%20her%20friend.%20Initially%2C%20both%20families%20thought%20the%20youngsters%20might%20have%20eloped%20as%20they%20seemed%20to%20be%20in%20love%20with%20each%20other.%20Luwangbi%20had%20mentioned%20visiting%20Nambol%20Bazar%20after%20class%2C%20but%20her%20phone%20went%20off%20after%20her%20last%20message%20from%20Khoupum%2C%20a%20Naga-dominated%20area%20about%2040%20km%20from%20the%20family%20home%2C%20according%20to%20her%20mother%2C%20Jayashree%20Devi.%20%E2%80%9CI%20kept%20trying%20to%20call%20her%20but%20it%20was%20switched%20off%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jayashree%20Devi%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFearing%20the%20worst%2C%20the%20family%20decided%20to%20file%20an%20FIR%20against%20Phijam%20Hemanjit%20Singh%2C%20although%20the%20police%20questioned%20them%20about%20turning%20a%20love%20story%20into%20a%20case%20since%20the%20girl%20was%20a%20minor.%20The%20FIR%20included%20charges%20of%20kidnapping%20and%20abduction%20with%20the%20intention%20to%20compel%20her%20into%20marriage%2C%20as%20per%20IPC%20Sections%20366%2C%20368%20and%2034.%20The%20FIR%20says%20Hemanjit%20is%2020%20years%20old%2C%20though%20his%20family%20says%20he%20is%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-capt