dwide%20fame%20by%20the%20Prince%20cover%20%E2%80%98Nothing%20Compares%202%20U%2C%E2%80%99%20which%20won%20the%201990%20Billboard%20Music%20Awards%20for%20Best%20Single%20in%20the%20World.%20The%20string-accompanied%20ballad%20topped%20the%20music%20charts%20from%20Europe%20to%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20had%20already%20received%20critical%20acclaim%20for%20her%20first%20album%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Lion%20and%20the%20Cobra%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20featuring%20her%20debut%20hit%20%E2%80%98Mandinka.%E2%80%99%20The%20singer%20released%2010%20studio%20albums%20in%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReaction%20to%20singer%E2%80%99s%20passing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVarious%20political%20figures%20and%20celebrities%20have%20been%20paying%20tribute%20to%20the%20singer%2C%20with%20Ireland%E2%80%99s%20President%20Michael%20D.Higgins%20saying%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20Ireland%20has%20lost%20at%20such%20a%20relatively%20young%20age%20is%20one%20of%20our%20greatest%20and%20most%20gifted%20composers%2C%20songwriters%20and%20performers%20of%20recent%20decades%2C%20one%20who%20had%20a%20unique%20talent%20and%20extraordinary%20connection%20with%20her%20audience%2C%20all%20of%20whom%20held%20such%20love%20and%20warmth%20for%20her.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIreland%E2%80%99s%20Prime%20Minister%20Leo%20Varadkar%20said%20O%E2%80%99Connor%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cmusic%20was%20loved%20around%20the%20world%20and%20her%20talent%20was%20unmatched%20and%20beyond%20compare.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIrish%20former%20UFC%20champion%20Conor%20McGregor%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20world%20has%20lost%20an%20artist%20with%20the%20voice%20of%20an%20angel.%20Ireland%20has%20lost%20an%20iconic%20voice%20and%20one%20of%20our%20absolute%20finest%2C%20by%20a%20long%20shot.%20And%20I%20have%20lost%20a%20friend.%20Sinead%E2%80%99s%20music%20will%20live%20on%20and%20continue%20to%20inspire!%20Rest%20In%20Peace%2C%20Sinead%20you%20are%20home%20with%20your%20son%20I%20am%20sure.%E2