ia%20after%20consuming%20cough%20syrup%20is%20back%20in%20the%20news%20again.%20These%20deaths%20were%20linked%20to%20four%20medicines%20made%20by%20an%20Indian%20manufacturer%2C%20Maiden%20Pharmaceuticals.%20A%20Gambian%20presidential%20task%20force%20has%20now%20recommended%20that%20the%20government%20must%20sue%20the%20drug%20manufacturer%2C%20Maiden%20Pharmaceuticals%2C%20and%20the%20drug%20importer%2C%20Atlantic%20Pharmaceuticals.%20It%20also%20wants%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20to%20be%20sued.%20This%20is%20perhaps%20the%20first%20instance%20where%20a%20foreign%20country%20has%20been%20recommended%20to%20take%20legal%20action%20against%20the%20Indian%20government.%20The%20government%20of%20Gambia%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20it%20would%20be%20suing%20both%20Maiden%20and%20Atlantic.%20It%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20made%20its%20stance%20on%20the%20Indian%20government%20clear%20but%20has%20maintained%20it%20would%20actively%20engage%20with%20it%20so%20that%20the%20victims%20the%20parents%20of%20the%20children%20who%20died%20get%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20have%20been%20at%20least%20four%20scientific%20reports%20previously%20that%20linked%20these%20deaths%20to%20Maiden%20Pharmaceutical%E2%80%99s%20products.%20Yet%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20has%20remained%20defiant%20and%20health%20minister%20Mansukh%20Mandaviya%20went%20on%20to%20say%20on%20a%20podcast%20recently%20that%20the%20kids%20died%20due%20to%20diarrhoea.%20Will%20this%20report%20nudge%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20act%3F%20Watch%20to%20know%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FQEB0rYIocq8%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690390835000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26221340%2FIMG_0324