n%20the%20esteemed%20way%20that%20many%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20US-based%20entrepreneur%20revealed%20that%20she%20is%20struggling%20to%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20the%20death%20of%20her%20ex-boyfriend%2C%20who%20died%20by%20suicide.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20having%20trouble%20bringing%20myself%20to%20date%20again%20for%20obvious%20reasons%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Mah%20acknowledged%20that%20one%20of%20her%20biggest%20problems%20is%20comparing%20herself%20to%20others.%20She%20admitted%20that%20she%20surrounds%20herself%20with%20highly%20successful%20people%20who%20have%20accomplished%20far%20more%20than%20she%20has%2C%20and%20whose%20net%20worth%20is%20higher%20than%20hers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BComparison%20is%20the%20thief%20of%20joy.%20I've%20learned%20that%20the%20hard%20way.%20But%20with%20a%20little%20trick%20I%20picked%20up%20in%20therapy%2C%20I%20find%20that%20I%20am%20comparing%20myself%20to%20others%20less%20and%20less%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20revealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20her%2C%20the%20trick%20is%20to%20%26quot%3Bthink%20about%20the%20bigger%20picture%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20see%20someone%20who%20seems%20to%20have%20a%20better%20lifestyle%20than%20you%2C%20think%20about%20the%20bigger%20picture.%20Would%20you%20truly%20trade%20places%20with%20them%3F%20If%20you%20compare%20yourself%20to%20someone%20else%2C%20you%20have%20to%20compare%20yourself%20to%20ALL%20of%20their%20struggles%2C%20too.%20And%20nobody%20is%20posting%20their%20insecurities%20and%20private%20challenges%20in%20the%20open%2C%20which%20is%20why%20I%20am!%26quot%3B%20she%20explained.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20remember%20to%20view%20those%20we%20envy%20with%20a%20wider%20lens%2C%20it's%20much%20easier%20to%20see%20that%20we%20are%20all%20flawed%20and%20come%20with%20our%20own%20sets%20of%20struggles%20and%20wins.%20Yours%20is%20likely%20no%20greater%20or%20worse%20than%20all%20of%20the%20rest%20of%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Mah%20concluded.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fbring-my-daughter-back-mother-of-hyderabad-woman-who-was-found-starving-on-us-street-4241540%5C%22%3E''Bring%20My%20Daughter%20Back''%3A%20Mother%20Of%20Hyderabad%20Woman%20Who%20Was%20Found%20Starving%20On%20US%20Street%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20her%20LinkedIn%20post%20has%20divided%20opinion%20on%20social%20media.%20While%20some%20applauded%20the%20entrepreneur%20for%20writing%20about%20her%20struggles%2C%20others%20said%20she%20failed%20to%20acknowledge%20her%20own%20privilege.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20really%20appreciate%20these%20posts%20and%20reminders.%20Especially%20the%20issue%20around%20comparison%2C%20which%20is%20such%20a%20big%20deal%20for%20entrepreneurs%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20one%20user.%20%26quot%3BI%20100%25%20agree%2C%20I%20think%20it%20takes%20a%20long%20time%20to%20be%20able%20to%20understand%20what%20makes%20you%20happy%20and%20enjoy%20the%20journey%20we%20are%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20another.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20one%20user%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20really%20typed%20all%20this%20and%20never%20once%20thought%20its%20a%20bad%20idea%20to%20post%20this%3F%20What%20even%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Baccomplishment%20dysmorphia%26quot%3B%3F%20Do%20you%20have%20some%20common%20sense%3F%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHahahahahahahahahahahahahahahaha%20how%20does%20one%20write%20something%20like%20this%20and%20completely%20fail%20to%20see%20the%20irony%2C%26quot%3B%20commented%20another.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20user%20even%20wrote%20that%C2%A0%26quot%3BAttempt%20at%20humble%20bragging%20just%20ends%20up%20being%20victimhood%20narcissism%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BUnhappy%20person%20still%20unhappy%20after%20wasting%20their%20life%20to%20become%20rich.%20What's%20new%3F%26quot%3B%20ask