y%20did%20not%20think%20anything%20of%20it.%20But%20when%20I%20explained%20how%20big%20the%20mountain%20was%2C%20they%20got%20excited%20and%20felt%20proud%20of%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarsha%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CTraining%20a%20seven-year-old%20can%20be%20tricky%20as%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20push%20them%20too%20hard.%20I%20sought%20advice%20from%20friends%20experienced%20in%20this%20area%20to%20understand%20how%20to%20prepare%20her%20for%20trekking%20high%20mountains.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20don%E2%80%99t%20really%20need%20a%20lot%20of%20space%20or%20equipment%20and%20can%20start%20with%20simple%20exercises%20to%20build%20strength.%20Eventually%2C%20we%20moved%20to%20high-intensity%20interval%20training%20too.%20Aadya%20was%20able%20to%20do%20the%20exercises%20effortlessly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRunning%2C%20long%20walks%20with%20a%20five-kilo%20backpack%2C%20stair%20climbing%2C%20and%20smaller%20treks%20within%20Karnataka%20were%20a%20part%20of%20Aadya%E2%80%99s%20routine%20training%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Harsha%20decided%20to%20take%20her%20to%20the%20Everest%20Base%20Camp%2C%20he%20did%20not%20receive%20the%20kind%20of%20reception%20he%20had%20hoped.%20%E2%80%9CEveryone%20including%20my%20family%2C%20parents%2C%20and%20friends%20said%20I%20was%20making%20a%20mistake.%20They%20were%20quite%20against%20the%20idea%20given%20that%20Aadya%20was%20quite%20young%20at%20that%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCeNTEIPvMpT%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCeNTEIPvMpT%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%