tterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel2-1690375407-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel2-1690375407-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel2-1690375407-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325207%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22816%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20trips%20usually%20have%206-10%20mothers%20and%20their%20children%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArmed%20with%20full-time%20jobs%2C%20Saakshi%20and%20Nikita%20do%20all%20the%20planning%20on%20weekends%2C%20when%20they%20also%20carry%20out%20recces%20of%20new%20locations%20for%20their%20next%20adventure.%20Their%20main%20goal%20is%20to%20empower%20mothers%20and%20help%20them%20come%20out%20of%20their%20comfort%20zones%20while%20giving%20their%20children%20a%20lot%20of%20new%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20giving%20birth%2C%20everyone%20tends%20to%20forget%20about%20the%20mother%20and%20focuses%20solely%20on%20the%20child.%20We%20want%20to%20prioritise%20the%20mother%20during%20the%20retreat.%20While%20we%20do%20cater%20to%20both%20the%20mother%20and%20child%2C%20we%20want%20to%20ensure%20the%20mother%E2%80%99s%20needs%20are%20not%20overlooked%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nikita%2C%20who%20is%20a%20full-time%20blogger%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGenerally%2C%20the%20trips%20are%20planned%20for%20two%20nights%20and%20three%20days%2C%20where%20the%20children%20can%20have%20fun%20while%20the%20mothers%20unwind.%20So%20far%2C%20their%20curated%20experiences%20have%20included%20farm-to-table%20dining%2C%20a%20mud%20bath%20in%20Goa%2C%20a%20sound%20garden%20in%20Puducherry%2C%20a%20crocodile%20bank%2C%20cooking%20classes%2C%20and%20dining%20by%20the%20beach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20USP%20of%20their%20venture%20is%20that%20one%20of%20the%20two%20founders%20is%20always%20present%20on%20the%20trip.%20They%20personally%20visit%20and%20explore%20the%20locations%20beforehand%2C%20along%20with%20their%20families%2C%20before%20planning%20it%20for%20others.%20They%20mostly%20book%20homestays%20or%20boutique%20hotels%20with%20kitchenettes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trips%20are%20usually%20priced%20around%20Rs%2020%2C000%E2%80%93Rs%2025%2C000%2C%20and%20each%20mother%20is%20given%20a%20separate%20room%20with%20her%20child%2Fchildren.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20816px)%20100vw%2C%20816px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel3-1690375408.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22816%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22travel%20with%20kids%20india%20takes%20mothers%20and%20children%20on%20trips%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel3-1690375408.jpg%20816w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel3-1690375408-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel3-1690375408-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel3-1690375408-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel3-1690375408-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel3-1690375408-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325208%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22816%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EChildren%20are%20usually%20between%20the%20age%20group%20of%202-12.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFirst%2C%20we%20form%20a%20WhatsApp%20group%20after%20people%20book%20the%20trip.%20We%20interact%20initially%20to%20understand%20the%20needs%20and%20eating%20habits%20of%20the%20moms%20and%20children%2C%20accommodating%20any%20special%20requirements%20through%20a%20detailed%20form.%20We%20also%20arrange%20Zoom%20calls%20for%20the%20moms%20to%20get%20to%20know%20each%20other%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Saakshi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20had%20mothers%20from%20Chennai%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Jaipur%2C%20Kochi%20and%20Kolkata%20join%20them%20on%20their%20trips%20so%20far.%20They%20are%20now%20working%20on%20going%20international%20next%20and%20currently%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F317592%2Ftravel-startup-wanderingjane-helps-plan-safe-solo-travel-for-women%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplanning%20some%20trips%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20North%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepika%2C%20who%20travelled%20with%20her%20seven-year-old%20son%20to%20Puducherry%20with%20Travel%20With%20Kids%20(India)%20says%20that%20they%20both%20had%20a%20fabulous%20time.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20entire%20trip%20was%20meticulously%20planned.%20On%20the%20way%20from%20Chennai%20to%20Pondicherry%2C%20we%20had%20a%20home-cooked%20meal%20which%20was%20made%20of%20ingredients%20straight%20from%20the%20farm.%20It%20was%20the%20first%20time%20that%20I%20had%20such%20food.%20Kiaan%20also%20enjoyed%20the%20crocodile%20bank%2C%20the%20cycle%20rickshaw%20drive%2C%20and%20the%20whole%20trip%20in%20general.%20I%20made%20a%20great%20friend%20with%20a%20fellow%20mom%20during%20the%20trip%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Deepika.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20safe%20haven%20for%20mothers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCtMQvK6goiA%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCtMQvK6goiA%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCtMQvK6goiA%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Travel%20with%20kids%20%7C%20India%20(%40travelwithkids_india)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20say%20that%20they%20are%20joined%20by%20a%20lot%20of%20single%20mothers%20on%20the%20trips.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20a%20supportive%20community%20of%20like-minded%20mothers%2C%20providing%20a%20non-judgemental%20space.%20Motherhood%20brings%20changes%20to%20all%20of%20us%2C%20and%20sometimes%20we%20may%20forget%20to%20prioritise%20ourselves.%20Many%20moms%20lose%20confidence%20in%20travelling%20alone%20with%20their%20kids.%20We%20want%20mothers%20to%20realise%20that%20they%20can%20still%20travel%2C%20albeit%20differently%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nikita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Nikita%20and%20Saakshi%2C%20some%20of%20the%20mothers%20who%20went%20on%20their%20trips%20have%20bonded%20so%20well%20that%20they%20now%20meet%20up%20regularly.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20all%20had%20similar%20experiences.%20We%20just%20need%20someone%20to%20talk%20to%20who%20has%20been%20through%20the%20same.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20everyone%20bonds%20so%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nikita%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThey%20want%20mothers%20across%20the%20country%20to%20travel%20with%20their%20children.%20%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201088px)%20100vw%2C%201088px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel4-1690375406.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221088%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22travel%20with%20kids%20india%20takes%20mothers%20and%20children%20on%20trips%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel4-1690375406.jpg%201088w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel4-1690375406-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel4-1690375406-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel4-1690375406-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel4-1690375406-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325206%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22816%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20duo%20has%20planned%2020%20trips%20so%20far.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20few%20tweaks%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20manageable%2C%20they%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20been%20to%20places%20which%20aren%E2%80%99t%20considered%20%E2%80%98kid-friendly%E2%80%99%20like%20Reunion%20Island%2C%20Morocco%20and%20Egypt.%20My%20daughter%20enjoyed%20it.%20Kids%20will%20always%20find%20a%20way%20to%20entertain%20themselves.%20You%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20always%20go%20to%20zoos%20or%20parks.%20It%E2%80%99s%20about%20the%20sensory%20experience%20of%20being%20in%20a%20new%20place%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Saakshi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFirst%20I%20travelled%20solo%2C%20then%20with%20my%20husband%20whose%20interests%20are%20very%20different.%20Now%20my%20children%E2%80%99s%20interests%20are%20different.%20You%20just%20have%20to%20cater%20to%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20needs%20as%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20manage%20their%20interests%20themselves.%20So%20you%20have%20to%20do%20it%20for%20them.%20But%20in%20this%20process%2C%20you%20get%20to%20see%20the%20world%20through%20their%20eyes%2C%20which%20is%20simply%20amazing.%20It%E2%80%99s%20different%2C%20but%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20like%20to%20exchange%20it%20for%20anything%2C%E2%80%9D%20smiles%20Nikita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20add%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F302712%2Fpuducherry-social-worker-helps-tribal-children-study-become-engineers-teachers-udhavi-karangal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDon%E2%80%99t%20let%20motherhood%3C%2Fa%3E%20become%20a%20barrier%20in%20pursuing%20your%20dreams.%20Believe%20in%20yourself%2C%20and%20sometimes%2C%20make%20yourself%20a%20priority.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20let%20anyone%20tell%20you%20that%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20travel%20or%20do%20anything%20you%20love%20after%20having%20a%20child.%20Take%20that%20plunge.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETo%20plan%20trips%20with%20the%20duo%2C%20you%20can%20contact%20them%20at%20%40travelwithkids_india%20on%20Instagram.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690378417000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel-with-kids3-1690375218.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D325192%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dr%20Saakshi%20Gulati%20and%20Dr%20Nikita%20Mathur%2C%20both%20dentists%20and%20avid%20travellers%2C%20started%20Travel%20with%20Kids%20(India)%20to%20encourage%20young%20mothers%20to%20fulfil%20their%20travel%20dreams%20with%20their%20children.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325192%2Fsaakshi-gulati-nikita-mathur-travel-with-ki