0playing%20in%20these%20spaces%20will%20facilitate%20their%20cognitive%20and%20behavioural%20development%20during%20early%20childhood.%20What%E2%80%99s%20also%20particularly%20encouraging%20is%20the%20minimal%20cost%20that%20went%20into%20building%20these%20playgrounds.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEducation%20should%20never%20be%20about%20textbook-based%20learning%20alone.%20The%20focus%20should%20be%20on%20the%20holistic%20development%20of%20children.%20Play%20is%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20overall%20growth%20of%20a%20child.%20We%20have%20been%20mandated%20to%20focus%20on%20early%20childhood%20development%20(ECD)%20by%20the%20Union%20and%20State%20government%20because%20this%20is%20the%20time%20when%20children%20learn%20the%20most%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FSnapinsta.app_171386959_474560363748134_6669212032293108365_n_1080-1689947152.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Innovate%20playgrounds%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FSnapinsta.app_171386959_474560363748134_6669212032293108365_n_1080-1689947152.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FSnapinsta.app_171386959_474560363748134_6669212032293108365_n_1080-1689947152-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FSnapinsta.app_171386959_474560363748134_6669212032293108365_n_1080-1689947152-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FSnapinsta.app_171386959_474560363748134_6669212032293108365_n_1080-1689947152-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FSnapinsta.app_171386959_474560363748134_6669212032293108365_n_1080-16899