200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fpixxel6-1689934894-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fpixxel6-1689934894-768x512.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fpixxel6-1689934894-1536x1023.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fpixxel6-1689934894-150x100.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fpixxel6-1689934894-272x182.jpeg%20272w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324704%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221066%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAwais%20Ahmed%20and%20Kshitij%20Khandelwal%2C%20Founders%20of%20Pixxel%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSatellite%20imagery%20seemed%20like%20an%20interesting%20area.%20I%20found%20that%20the%20existing%20satellite%20data%20was%20good%2C%20but%20not%20good%20enough%20in%20many%20use%20cases.%20For%20instance%2C%20it%20can%E2%80%99t%20detect%20underground%20oil%20leaks%2C%20identify%20species%20and%20subspecies%20of%20crops%20and%20trees%2C%20or%20detect%20effluents%20and%20their%20composition%20in%20water%20bodies.%20I%20knew%20that%20it%20could%20be%20much%20better.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20zeroed%20in%20on%20hyperspectral%20imaging%20satellites%20and%20launched%20Pixxel%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202019%2C%20Awais%20co-founded%20Pixxel%20along%20with%20Kshitij%20Khandelwal%20and%20two%20other%20engineers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20goal%20is%20to%20create%20and%20launch%20a%20group%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F304203%2Fbengaluru-startup-pixxel-launches-anand-hyperspectral-satellite-isro-pslv-rocket%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadvanced%20imaging%20satellites%3C%2Fa%3E%20called%20hyperspectral%20imaging%20satellites.%20T