%2C%20he%20called%20to%20reassure%20her%20that%20he%20would%20be%20back%20the%20next%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20asked%20me%20to%20prepare%20%3Cem%3Eurad%20daal%20paratha%20%3C%2Fem%3E(flat%20bread%20stuffed%20with%20black%20lentils).%20I%20had%20kept%20the%20filling%20and%20dough%20ready%20the%20next%20morning.%20But%20then%20I%20received%20a%20call%20and%20my%20life%20was%20shattered%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20told%20me%20that%20he%20was%20no%20more.%20My%20husband%20was%20murdered%20in%20a%20conspiracy%20for%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CLosing%20him%20was%20so%20painful.%20I%20had%20lost%20all%20hope%20to%20live%2C%20but%20I%20had%20two%20sons%20to%20look%20after.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShashi%E2%80%99s%20sons%20were%20aged%20five%20and%20seven%20years%20when%20her%20husband%20died%20in%202001.%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20have%20enough%20money%20to%20even%20arrange%20for%20%3Cem%3Epagdi%20dastoor%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20Rajasthani%20tradition%20wherein%20responsibilities%20of%20the%20dead%20are%20passed%20to%20their%20son).%20We%20survived%20on%20%3Cem%3Enamak%20mirch%20roti%20%3C%2Fem%3E(flatbread%20with%20chilly%20and%20salt)%20for%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-3-1689859353.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shashi%E2%80%99s%20sons%20were%20aged%20five%20and%20seven%20years%20when%20her%20husband%20died.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-3-1689859353.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-3-1689859353-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A