rops%20like%20lettuce%2C%20up%20to%2015%20degrees%20Celsius.%20We%20use%20urban%20clay%20pots%20to%20regulate%20the%20temperature%20of%20water%20in%20the%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faquaponics-1689666293.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shashank%20says%20it%20costs%20Rs%20800%20per%20sq%20ft%20to%20establish%20an%20aquaponics%20terrace%20farm%20in%20a%20vertical%20setup.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faquaponics-1689666293.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faquaponics-1689666293-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faquaponics-1689666293-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faquaponics-1689666293-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faquaponics-1689666293-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324146%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShashank%20says%20it%20costs%20Rs%20800%20per%20sq%20ft%20to%20establish%20an%20aquaponics%20terrace%20farm%20in%20a%20vertical%20setup.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20this%2C%20he%20suggests%20farmers%20introduce%20fish%20like%20gold%20and%20koi%20fish.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20produce%20more%20excreta%20and%20also%20survive%20in%20harsh%20temperature%20conditions.%20Just%20ensure%20to%20filter%20the%20water%20before%20adding%20the%20fish%20to%20the%20tank%3B%20water%20should%20not%20be%20hard.%20You%20can%20add%20150%20fish%20in%20a%201%2C000-litre%20tank.%20For%20edible%20fish%2C%20you%20would%20require%20a%20tank%20of%203%2C000%20litres%20as%20their%20si